{"tid":1296651,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[廣東檢討] 知唔知大Sir Rupert Dover 尋日點樣喺廣東道逃脫？","createTime":"2019-07-08T12:19:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T12:49:33.000Z","uid":194573,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1d5bb4b4f20cad7587ec90aae97be5d31d4bc2e8","tid":1296651,"uid":194573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T12:19:41.000Z","msg":"可能無乜人留意8點嘅廣東道<br />\n<br />\n發夢喺1881高空觀察<br />\n見到Dover大狗首先被圍<br />\n<br />\n班狗小組討論咗一陣<br />\nDover聯同成班PC仔向天星碼頭方向行<br />\n後排有堆CID 組成第二排人鏈 <br />\n分開示威者同大狗距離<br />\n<br />\n之後<br />\n1. 有個八婆CID出警棍撩港台記者<br />\n2. 又有另一個八婆CID 大嗌<br />\n3. 仲有個呀叔扮示威者 助攻比PC狗插水跌落地<br />\n兄弟當然分別地起哂哄<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">趁我哋起哄之際 大狗輕鬆走佬<br />\n前後用咗三招 為咗調虎離山</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n無幾耐大狗Rupert Dover 輕鬆去天星碼頭<br />\nSpare返啲PC狗返後場幫拖<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咁用咗呢三招 分散哂我哋注意力</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我只想講 現場點樣兄弟行動 點都要有個揸咪嘅做觀察員 兄弟都要有大局觀</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山 各自努力<br />\n不割分篤<br />\n<br />\n利申：尋晚打緊Sleeping Dogs"},{"pid":"c1ac79edc745640fb5c716816e9b8be3c32ea623","tid":1296651,"uid":194573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T12:22:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>廣東<span style=\"color: red;\">道</span>檢討</blockquote>"},{"pid":"a50df7cfa637609c98384897d73e40fce48ae12d","tid":1296651,"uid":166947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T12:22:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"50780e4868edf367792798523bf7fbf01d27f607","tid":1296651,"uid":194573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T12:24:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f076049327d7c23e1b0851175806e34405606686","tid":1296651,"uid":194573,"like":0,